online.common
Interface exHashtable

public interface exHashtable

extended hash table. Contents are typed. Error if null is retrieved from a typed fetch, or if a typed put would clobber an existing key. This class is intended to serve as a repository of shared context between cooperating frames.

the many static strings associated with this class are the expected key names. Using these keywords rather than random strings makes it easy to find where the keys are used, and also prevents "typo" class bugs.
